===message:I tend to disagree with you.  I don’t think that the South’s strongest slavery supporters would have abolished slavery if not forced.  I am not sure the Industrial Revolution would have stopped the profitability of slavery.  Blacks were not equal to whites in any shape, form or fashion in this time frame.  What would the blacks have done if not encompassed by slavery?  They sure would have not gotten paid for their labor in the cotton fields and nobody considered smart enough to do much else.
